description:
• You will use this course like a road-map for your testing career before you attend any interview.
  • We'll sit and revise all the software testing concepts that can be asked during your interviews.
  • At the end of this course, you will gain confidence in how to crack any testing interview.
  • This course covers all the FAQs that are generally asked during testing interview for freshers/beginners and also discusses how to answer the questions.
title: Let's Crack Manual Testing Interview (Part-1)
